Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Feelings (Continued)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anti-bullying measures?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wh-What's wrong, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Tell me everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, I'm on your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No, it's not about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you want to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. In the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm not being bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm just being ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any friends. Or more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:11.75,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLUNT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in anyone's field of vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SLAP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, never mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a professional at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I've been eating lunch\Nby myself for over 11 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SPARKLE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Professional? In what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kiriyama!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. A third-year middle school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In a family that's helped you out a lot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, it's a shame about that other girl\Nwho switched schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I think she was really lucky\Nto have someone like Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Otherwise, it could have had a sadder ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:03:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's actually really important that Hina\Nwas able to talk to her family about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The worst thing anyone could do\Nis not talk about it, and keep it bottled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not talk to their family or their teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when it came to her friend, Chiho,\Nshe told her homeroom teacher about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she got brushed off, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher said she was\N"misreading the situation."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! So she's that type\Nof homeroom teacher, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She got stuck with one of those. Poor kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was probably desperate\Nwhen she asked for advice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can get the teacher's perspective,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but that's no time to be running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought I would ask your opinion\Nto get the school's perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}UGH
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}JEEZ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}UGH
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}JEEZ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}UGH
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}JEEZ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you could give me a hint\Non how to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BULLYING
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}School bullying problems getting worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Severe bullying. Please talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you do a search on "bullying,"\Nyou'll get 89,100,000 hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do a search for "bullying countermeasures,"\Nand you get 2,200,000 hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And nowhere in here is a solution\Nthat'll work 100% of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this homepage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People who are being bullied.\NPeople who are doing the bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The parents of both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People who saw it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People who were bullied in the past.\NPeople who were bullies in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That teacher could scroll through\N200 million pages
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,from several years and encounter\Na mess of muddled arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, there are thousands\Nof sites like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mr. Hayashida? Mr. Hayashida...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you won't find an answer in any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there's a distinct "answer"\Nfor every one of these people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a quandary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People who want an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People who want to defend themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Parents who want to avenge their children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Parents who want to clear\Ntheir children's names.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People who want their bullies\Nto get the same treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People who want to return\Nto their circle of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The configurations of the positions and\Npersonalities of people involved are all different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why there's no "perfect answer"\Nthat can work for every case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean you should give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you think, "there's no answer\Nto be found so I'll do nothing,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...then you'll get nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But at least we've come to know\Nwhat not to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's to stir everyone up with cries of\N"We have to solve this,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,while ignoring the victim's feelings,\Nand moving ahead too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I say your daughter is the one who's lying!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My kid said she didn't do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your daughter's obviously a delinquent!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's tormented the hell out of my daughter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Um, I've distributed surveys throughout\Nthe school about whether bullying is going on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- There's no need for that!\N- You're going to pay for this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, stop! Stop! Please stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the victim doesn't want to make a big deal\Nout of it, or even get more people involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then it's wrong for the families to cause a commotion\Nat school, even if it solves the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I heard she was bullied during second year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The whole school got involved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because even if the bullying died down,\Nif they feel out of place there,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then it was all for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the important thing is to ask Hina\Nabout what kind of solution she's hoping for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's okay if this takes time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}so be sure to listen patiently\Nto all of her feelings on the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I see. Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}SCRIBBLE SCRIBBLE\NNOTE NOTE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But actually, what's surprisingly effective\Nis being able to say "Stop it"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when the bully does something to them\Nright then and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That all rides on whether\Nshe's the type of person who can say that or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}She's really energetic, with a loud voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}She laughs a lot,\Nand gets angry or dejected easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You could say she's relatively complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And pretty vain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And for someone who's so cheerful,\Nshe doesn't have much confidence in herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she's strong at heart. Very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kiriyama's been watching her closely, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could this be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it possibly be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a flag?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh. You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, um... Uh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm just asking for data purposes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so, in what way is she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, she has big eyes, small, thin arms and legs,\Nlong, glossy hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:51.15,DefaultLef2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CREAK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:51.15,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NERVOUS\NNERVOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And then there's this,\Nto confirm, just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Um, about that girl... How can I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I-Is she important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She's very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BLUNT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to do anything I can for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Diving into the atmosphere of adolescence!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kiriyama!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If she's in trouble,\NI want to do anything I can to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she's my lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I have an obligation to pay her back.\NThat's my duty as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Um, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Kind of has a bad feeling about this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HOME TUTORING
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I got carried away there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, you were fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was thrilled to see\Na new side of you, Kiriyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HEAPS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}280,000 per month x 9 months\NTotal 2,520,000
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shishi-ou Tournament\NTotal\N3,600,000 ~ 8,000,000
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... And what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bracket for a shogi tournament, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe all of these scrawled numbers are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Total: 3,600,000-8,000,000
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Total: 1,500,000
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...money from matches?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, but since I was making a proposal,\Nand if I didn't hold it down to realistic figures,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it would just be irresponsible lip service.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have a debt to repay,\Nso I just can't be dreaming all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good. My calculator still works.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...from this point on,\NI can't afford to lose any matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Serious Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I can't afford to lose any matches."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wood Carving
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that what you said without any hesitation?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's about time for my workshop.\NI have to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mr. Hayashida!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thank you very much for your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's given me food for thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I would appreciate it\Nif we could talk again about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}He's a little off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}This kid is just off about something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}That's what the teacher's heart\Nwas yelling out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I have to check!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to put my life as a teacher on the line\Nand do something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Before Kiriyama takes those documents\Nto her house and makes a speech!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Otherwise he's going to lose her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Rei Kiriyama, 5th dan, 18 years old,\Nwith calculator in hand, will intervene{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}in the life of that girl\Nto whom he owes a debt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! What am I going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would Hayashida,\Nhis homeroom teacher from last year,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}be able to stop him from running amok?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stay tuned and you'll find out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Confession
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What's wrong with Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I've never seen him this frustrated\Nafter losing before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Finally...\NDoes he finally have the motivation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}QUIVER QUIVER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Has he come around to the idea\Nof burning together
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}in the surging flames of passion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kiriyama, welcome to the world\Nof bosom buddies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOOD
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GRIND GRIND GRIND
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One more win and I would've gone to\Nthe semifinals, where the pay gets doubled!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it! I'm an idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GRIND GRIND GRIND
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Were you just talking big\Nabout the debt repayment, Rei Kiriyama?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}If something happens\Nand she ends up going to another school,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}or she stops going\Nand has to rely on private tutors,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}or consults with a lawyer,\Nall of these things take money!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whatever happens to Hina,\Nit's my job to prepare a place for her to go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nikaidou! Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What is it, best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:13:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I need to practice. Would you play me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Of course, my best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BEST FRIEND
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you, Nikaidou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GOOD
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Is my place okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Anywhere works for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wherever there's a board and pieces,\Nthat's our battlefield, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten matches with\Na 30-minute time limit per move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall behind, Nikaidou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose at the next Kishousen Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:28.93,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MONEY DEBT MONEY\NMONEY SHOGI MONEY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:28.93,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inside Kiriyama's Brain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In fact, I can't lose a single match!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:31.47,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BEST FRIENDS BEST FRIENDS\NBEST FRIENDS SHOGI BEST FRIENDS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:31.47,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inside Nikaidou's Brain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kiriyama, those words are music to my ears!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's tough. Everything is tough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reality is tough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that doesn't mean I can give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how it's been up to now,\Nand, of course, that's how it'll always be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But right now, I'm doing it for Hina!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}That Sunday, I got a text from Akari.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,POTATOES\NONIONS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thanks, Kiriyama. This is a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all. This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They had so many special sales\Nto celebrate their remodeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HEAVY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WOBBLE\NWOBBLE...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, just 200 yen\Nfor a box of potatoes or onions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't pass that up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And then there was 100 grams\Nof chicken thigh for 48 yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}MARU S\NSPECIAL SALE TODAY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}99 yen for a tub of margarine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}100 grams of pork for 126 yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}99 yen for a carton of milk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, I'm overjoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Hina today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's at the amusement park in Asakusa\Nwith Grandpa and Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}THREE LITTLE PIGS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's still feeling a little down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So Grandpa took her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope this will help her to feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Panda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, Kiriyama, are you okay with those?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Want me to take one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Really? Are you sure they're not too heavy?\NDon't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's okay. I am a guy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei doesn't seem to be getting fluffy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I worry about you.\NHow many kilos are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,52 kg...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}FREEZE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, please wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be on my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I'm always intruding...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HESITANT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it kind of seems like you're angry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to make me break down\Nthese vegetables by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. For starters,\Npeel the outer layer off of all these onions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After that,\Nremove the strings from the string beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you done it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You didn't do a single thing wrong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You helped your friend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be proud of yourself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:17:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa made a strong declaration like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hina...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sis, what should I have done?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hesitated that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't say something to Hina\Nlike Grandpa did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Far from it. I asked her, "Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Why didn't you tell me this before?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Why couldn't you have handled it\Nmore smoothly?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa told me this afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought the same thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think of the safety of a kid in my own family\Nbefore a kid in another family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's only natural. Everyone is that way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}But think about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Did Hina do anything wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}No, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hina is suffering plenty as it is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So if we ask her, "Why did you do that?"\Non top of everything else, she'll feel lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}More than anything,\Nshouldn't we praise Hina for her courage{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}and sense of justice for standing by her friend,\Neven though she knew{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}it might make her the next target?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since our Mom died,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been the surrogate mom\Nfor Hina and Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know anything at 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Mom was counting on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I tried as hard as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Think about the people\Nwho are around you, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Be kind to people."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been pushing ham-fisted advice on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when push came to shove,\Nthis is what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "I don't care about justice.\NI just wanted her to run away."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Hina was hanging in there\Nfor the sake of her friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You... You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What you felt was normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one wants a family member\Nto go through a painful experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the one\Nwho's been watching over Hina the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is you, Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been alone ever since I was a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the thought of someone extending\Na helping hand was so terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't ask for anyone's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that day,\Neven though Hina said she was scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she was just as certain that she had "no regrets"\Nand "didn't do anything wrong."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she was trying to convince herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I realized that she had saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That Hina was my savior...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:21:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you, who raised Hina to be a girl\Nwith so much courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're my savior too, Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is curry all right for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I should make a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'll come home hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guess what?! Pikatoo was there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}RAWRR
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I rode on a panda!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait, Momo!\NYou need to take your shoes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hold still now!\N- Oh, it's Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck, kid? You're here today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you visit too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:21:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take me seriously, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pain in the neck. Eat, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're making me look like a bad guy here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won it at a ball toss game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it looked like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might be childish, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No, I'm touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Okay, wash your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.41,0:22:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Confession
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:37.97,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 28
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.64,0:24:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherries!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.39,0:24:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama came to have\Ninstructional matches with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.68,0:24:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's called communicating, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.85,0:24:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, are you sure\Nthat's all you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.27,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me about your school?\NIt can be about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.03,0:24:58.50,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ILLUSTRATION:\NBUKUBU OHKAWA
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.65,0:24:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama! I've been waiting\Nfor you to become passionate!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.16,0:24:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accompany you\Nuntil the very end!
